body:
### Hey There!
Welcome to Geobot 9000! This will probably turn into a log about making stuff in a tiny one-car garage. 

### About Me
I am a tinkerer based in Las Vegas, NV. I enjoy discussing the benefits of boxer briefs and stopping into Little Caesars on my way to the gym. 

### What I Make
Expect to see this page updated soon with snippets featuring: a benchtop CNC router complete with exploding end mills, learning Fusion 360, aluminum sand casting including collapsing molds, and the occasional dollar store meal.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
